title: Was Kyle Rittenhouse at the Trump Club?
subtitle: A 17-year-old boy accused of murder in the first degree after the murder of two demonstrators in Kenosha, Wisconsin, was published in the social media to support the issue of blue life and President Trump.
author: Dan Evon
vclaim: Kyle Rittenhouse, 17, accused of killing two people in a protest in Wisconsin, attended a demonstration by President Trump.
